query:
INSERT INTO dependence_chain(
                    dependence_chain_id,
                    status,
                    last_updated_at,
                    dependency_count,
                    dependents,
                    block_hash,
                    block_height
                ) VALUES (
                  $1, 'updated', $2::timestamp, $3, $4, $5, $6
                )
                ON CONFLICT (dependence_chain_id) DO UPDATE
                SET status = 'updated'
